definitions.definition: The third son of Noah , brother to Shem and Ham , who received a blessing from God with Shem, considered to be the ancestor of the Japhetic people (s) ( associated approx. with Indo-Europeans ) .
A male given name from Hebrew of biblical origin.

main_definition: ( biblical ) The third son of Noah , brother to Shem and Ham , who received a blessing from God with Shem, considered to be the ancestor of the Japhetic people (s) ( associated approx. with Indo-Europeans ) .
